OL,3,CCrisis-hit HMP Wandsworth most
OL,4,Covercrowded prison in the country
OL,6,FScandal-hit HMP Wandsworth is the most
OL,7,Fovercrowded prison in the country,
OL,8,Fdata shows.
OL,10,FThe Victorian jail is holding 62% more
OL,11,Fpeople than it is designed for,
OL,12,Faccording to figures from the Ministry
OL,13,Fof Justice.
OL,15,FWandsworth, one of the largest prisons
OL,16,Fin the UK, currently has 1,444 inmates
OL,17,Fwhen it should only hold 894.
OL,19,FConditions inside the category B
OL,20,Fprison have been described as
OL,21,F"inhumane".
OL,26,@}D@AOU}D@JO]
