CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777389066
OL,3,CCrisis-hit HMP Wandsworth most
OL,4,Covercrowded prison in the country
OL,6,FThe chaos at the south-west London
OL,7,Fprison has been laid bare through a
OL,8,Fseries of high-profile incidents in
OL,9,Frecent years.
OL,11,FAccording to the Howard League for
OL,12,FPenal Reform, Category B prisons tend
OL,13,Fto be the most overcrowded, with a
OL,14,F"constantly churning population".
OL,16,FPrisons fit more people in by cramming
OL,17,Ftwo inmates into single cells, or
OL,18,Fthree into cells intended for only two
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
