OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777389066
OL,3,CCrisis-hit HMP Wandsworth most
OL,4,Covercrowded prison in the country
OL,6,FAccording to the latest available
OL,7,Ffigures from March, Wandsworth is
OL,8,Fclosely followed by HMP Leeds (61%
OL,9,Fmore prisoners than it is designed
OL,10,Ffor), and HMP Durham (59%).
OL,12,FIn September 2023, former soldier
OL,13,FDaniel Khalife, later found guilty of
OL,14,Fspying for Iran, escaped from the
OL,15,Fprison by clinging to the underside of
OL,16,Fa food delivery truck.
OL,18,FHe was caught on a canal towpath by a
OL,19,Fplainclothes detective days later.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
