OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777389066
OL,3,CCrisis-hit HMP Wandsworth most
OL,4,Covercrowded prison in the country
OL,6,FThe mistaken release of Algerian
OL,7,Fnational Brahim Kaddour-Cherif put HMP
OL,8,FWandsworth back in the headlines last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FAlso in 2025, former Wandsworth prison
OL,12,Fofficer Linda De Sousa Abreu was
OL,13,Fjailed for 15 months after having sex
OL,14,Fwith an inmate in a cell.
OL,16,FFootage of the activity was widely
OL,17,Fshared on social media.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
