OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777389066
OL,3,CCrisis-hit HMP Wandsworth most
OL,4,Covercrowded prison in the country
OL,6,FThe prison was put into special
OL,7,Fmeasures in 2024 as one of 10 jails
OL,8,Fissued with an urgent notice to
OL,9,Fimprove since November 2022.
OL,11,FInspectors said the turmoil they found
OL,12,Fwas the result of "sustained decline
OL,13,Fpermitted to happen in plain view of
OL,14,Fleaders", and prison guards did not
OL,15,Falways know where prisoners on their
OL,16,Fwings were, despite an investment of
OL,17,Falmost #900,000 since the escape.
OL,26,@tD@SOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
