OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1777389066
OL,3,CCrisis-hit HMP Wandsworth most
OL,4,Covercrowded prison in the country
OL,6,FBut in the latest review of the prison
OL,7,Fin April last year, the watchdog noted
OL,8,Fa new governor has brought "energy and
OL,9,Ffocus" and was prioritising safety and
OL,10,Fdecency.
OL,12,FInspectors found "substantial
OL,13,Finvestment" in staffing and training
OL,14,Fbut overall level of experience was
OL,15,Flow.
OL,17,FIn October, a further report by the
OL,18,Fprisons independent monitoring board
OL,19,Ffound staffing was a recurrent
OL,20,Fproblem, with an average of a third of
OL,21,Fstaff absent a day.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@FO]tD@ROUuD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
